snippet.textDisplay:
So even in the full game, Difficulty Selection is locked behind the 1st Boss? Fk this piece of shit game. I've seen Souls Clones pull alot of 80s fake challenge bs that's worse than what FromSoft has ever done, but locking Difficulty Selection behind ANYTHING takes the cake.

So unnecessary too. The game wouldn't be frustrating & it'd be player's choice if they want to torture themselves or not, if Difficulty Selection was at the very start LIKE ANY NORMAL GAME!

Fuck these devs that keep copying FS & do worse things. Its not like these Niche ass games will ever sell. And before anyone mentions Elden Ring, the DLC playercount in its first week being just 5mil, proves once & for all that Souls is niche.

I don't see the point of non-Indie devs, making games for a puny audience.

What's next? One of those handicap runs like No Rolling or No Armor, being MANDATORY for the first area, up to the first boss?
